<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-51-0548 </DOCNO><TEXT>This paper outlines a recently started research project with the aim ofanalysing the demand for natural gas and gas trade in Western Europewith special attention paid to the role of Norway as a gas supplier.It reviews plans of a natural gas demand model and a gas trade modelfor the European gas market. The models suggested in this paper willbe made operational through 1984 and 1985, and are intended to serveresearch purposes as well as administrative use. The project is alsoa contribution to IIASA's international gas study.</TEXT></DOC>